Author: 1anadelbae
Text: I’m glad your sister supports you, stay safe!

Author: PsychologicalUse1
Text: my sister once called me “waifishly pretty.” it was at my lowest weight, & to this day remains the best compliment I’ve ever received.  it was before she knew about my ED and she’s incredibly supportive and loving but oh my god thinking about it makes me want to relapse like no other.
